{"id":824,"parent_id":822,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":824,"title":"Lamentations 2","subtitle":"","short_title":"Lam.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 2"],[".studySummary",["i","Misery, sorrow, and desolation prevail in Jerusalem."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.1","order":"02.26.002.54660"},["b","1"],"How hath the Lord covered the daughter of Zion with a cloud in his anger,",["i","and"],"cast down from heaven unto the earth the beauty of Israel, and remembered not his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"footstool"],"in the day of his anger!"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.2","order":"02.26.002.54661"},["b","2"],"The Lord hath swallowed up all the habitations of Jacob, and hath not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"pitied"],": he hath thrown down in his wrath the strong holds of the daughter of Judah; he hath brought",["i","them"],"down to the ground: he hath polluted the kingdom and the princes thereof."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.3","order":"02.26.002.54662"},["b","3"],"He hath cut off in",["i","his"],"fierce anger all the horn of Israel: he hath",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"drawn"],"back his right hand from before the enemy, and he",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"burned"],"against Jacob like a flaming fire,",["i","which"],"devoureth round about."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.4","order":"02.26.002.54663"},["b","4"],"He hath bent his bow like an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"enemy"],": he stood with his right hand as an adversary, and slew all",["i","that were"],"pleasant to the eye in the tabernacle of the daughter of Zion: he poured out his fury like fire."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.5","order":"02.26.002.54664"},["b","5"],"The Lord was as an enemy: he hath swallowed up Israel, he hath swallowed up all her palaces: he hath destroyed his strong holds, and hath increased in the daughter of Judah",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"mourning"],"and lamentation."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.6","order":"02.26.002.54665"},["b","6"],"And he hath violently taken away his tabernacle, as",["i","if it were of"],"a garden: he hath destroyed his places of the assembly: the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath caused the solemn feasts and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"sabbaths"],"to be forgotten in Zion, and hath despised in the indignation of his anger the king and the priest."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.7","order":"02.26.002.54666"},["b","7"],"The Lord hath cast off his altar, he hath abhorred his sanctuary, he hath given up into the hand of the enemy the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"walls"],"of her palaces; they have made a noise in the house of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", as in the day of a solemn feast."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.8","order":"02.26.002.54667"},["b","8"],"The",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath purposed to destroy the wall of the daughter of Zion: he hath stretched out a line, he hath not withdrawn his hand from destroying: therefore he made the rampart and the wall to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"lament"],"; they languished together."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.9","order":"02.26.002.54668"},["b","9"],"Her",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"gates"],"are sunk into the ground; he hath destroyed and broken her bars: her king and her princes",["i","are"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"among"],"the Gentiles: the law",["i","is"],"no",["i","more;"],"her",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"prophets"],"also find no",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_9d"},"vision"],"from the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.10","order":"02.26.002.54669"},["b","10"],"The elders of the daughter of Zion sit upon the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"ground"],",",["i","and"],"keep",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"silence"],": they have cast up dust upon their heads; they have girded themselves with",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"sackcloth"],": the virgins of Jerusalem hang down their heads to the ground."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.11","order":"02.26.002.54670"},["b","11"],"Mine eyes do fail with",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"tears"],", my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"bowels"],"are troubled, my liver is poured upon the earth, for the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"destruction"],"of the daughter of my people; because the children and the sucklings swoon in the streets of the city."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.12","order":"02.26.002.54671"},["b","12"],"They say to their mothers, Where",["i","is"],"corn and wine? when they swooned as the wounded in the streets of the city, when their soul was poured out into their mothers’ bosom."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.13","order":"02.26.002.54672"},["b","13"],"What thing shall I take to witness for thee? what thing shall I liken to thee, O daughter of Jerusalem? what shall I equal to thee, that I may comfort thee, O",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"virgin"],"daughter of Zion? for thy breach",["i","is"],"great like the sea: who can heal thee?"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.14","order":"02.26.002.54673"},["b","14"],"Thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"prophets"],"have seen",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"vain"],"and foolish things for thee: and they have not discovered thine iniquity, to turn away thy captivity; but have seen for thee false burdens and causes of banishment."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.15","order":"02.26.002.54674"},["b","15"],"All that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"pass"],"by",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"clap"],["i","their"],"hands at thee; they hiss and wag their head at the daughter of Jerusalem,",["i","saying, Is"],"this the city that",["i","men"],"call The",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_15c"},"perfection"],"of",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_15d"},"beauty"],", The",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_15e"},"joy"],"of the whole earth?"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.16","order":"02.26.002.54675"},["b","16"],"All thine",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"enemies"],"have opened their mouth against thee: they",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"hiss"],"and gnash the teeth: they say, We have swallowed",["i","her"],"up: certainly this",["i","is"],"the day that we looked for; we have found, we have seen",["i","it."]],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.17","order":"02.26.002.54676"},["b","17"],"The",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath done",["i","that"],"which he had",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"devised"],"; he hath fulfilled his word that he had commanded in the days of old: he hath thrown down, and hath not pitied: and he hath caused",["i","thine"],"enemy to rejoice over thee, he hath set up the horn of thine adversaries."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.18","order":"02.26.002.54677"},["b","18"],"Their heart cried unto the Lord, O wall of the daughter of Zion, let tears run down like a river day and night: give thyself no rest; let not the apple of thine eye cease."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.19","order":"02.26.002.54678"},["b","19"],"Arise, cry out in the night: in the beginning of the watches pour out thine heart like water before the face of the Lord: lift up thy hands toward him for the life of thy young children, that faint for hunger in the top of every street."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.20","order":"02.26.002.54679"},["b","20"],"¶Behold, O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and consider to whom thou hast done this. Shall the women",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"eat"],"their fruit,",["i","and"],"children of a span long? shall the priest and the prophet be slain in the sanctuary of the Lord?"],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.21","order":"02.26.002.54680"},["b","21"],"The young and the old lie on the ground in the streets: my virgins and my young men are fallen by the sword; thou hast",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"slain"],["i","them"],"in the day of thine anger; thou hast killed,",["i","and"],"not pitied."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.22","order":"02.26.002.54681"},["b","22"],"Thou hast called as in a solemn day my terrors round about, so that in the day of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"’s anger none escaped nor remained: those that I have swaddled and brought up hath mine enemy consumed."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.1a","order":"02.26.002.54682"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/28.2"},"1 Chr. 28:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/17.39"},"1 Ne. 17:39"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.17"},"D&C 38:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/abr/2.7"},"Abr. 2:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.2a","order":"02.26.002.54684"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/23.18"},"2 Ne. 23:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.3a","order":"02.26.002.54686"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/74.11"},"Ps. 74:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.3b","order":"02.26.002.54688"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/5.26"},"Jacob 5:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.4a","order":"02.26.002.54690"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.10.9-10"},"Isa. 63:10 (9–10)"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.5a","order":"02.26.002.54692"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mourning"},"TG Mourning"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.6a","order":"02.26.002.54694"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/1.13.13-14"},"Isa. 1:13 (13–14)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.7a","order":"02.26.002.54696"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/5.5.4-5"},"Isa. 5:5 (4–5)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.8a","order":"02.26.002.54698"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/3.26"},"Isa. 3:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.9a","order":"02.26.002.54700"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/3.26"},"Isa. 3:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.9b","order":"02.26.002.54702"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/23.15"},"2 Ne. 23:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/59.6.5-6"},"Alma 59:6 (5–6)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.9c","order":"02.26.002.54704"},["b","9c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/74.9"},"Ps. 74:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"9d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.9d","order":"02.26.002.54706"},["b","9d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/revelation"},"TG Revelation"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.10a","order":"02.26.002.54708"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/3.26.24-26"},"Isa. 3:26 (24–26)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.10b","order":"02.26.002.54710"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.12.11-12"},"D&C 38:12 (11–12)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.10c","order":"02.26.002.54712"},["b","10c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.18"},"Ezek. 7:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.11a","order":"02.26.002.54714"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/6.18.17-22"},"Morm. 6:18 (17–22)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.11b","order":"02.26.002.54716"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.20"},"Lam. 1:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"11c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.11c","order":"02.26.002.54718"},["b","11c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/3.48"},"Lam. 3:48"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.13a","order":"02.26.002.54720"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/19.21"},"2 Kgs. 19:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.14a","order":"02.26.002.54722"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/false-prophets"},"TG False Prophets"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.14b","order":"02.26.002.54724"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/13.27.27-29"},"Hel. 13:27 (27–29)"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.15a","order":"02.26.002.54726"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.14"},"Ezek. 5:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.15b","order":"02.26.002.54728"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/job/27.23"},"Job 27:23"],"."],["div",{"id":"15c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.15c","order":"02.26.002.54730"},["b","15c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/50.2"},"Ps. 50:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/16.14"},"Ezek. 16:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"15d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.15d","order":"02.26.002.54732"},["b","15d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/27.3"},"Ezek. 27:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/28.12"},"28:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"15e","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.15e","order":"02.26.002.54734"},["b","15e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/48.2"},"Ps. 48:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.16a","order":"02.26.002.54736"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/3.46.46-51"},"Lam. 3:46 (46–51)"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.16b","order":"02.26.002.54738"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/16.9"},"3 Ne. 16:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.17a","order":"02.26.002.54740"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zech/1.6"},"Zech. 1:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.20a","order":"02.26.002.54742"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.9"},"Jer. 19:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.10"},"Ezek. 5:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.21a","order":"02.26.002.54744"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/36.17"},"2 Chr. 36:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/14.18"},"Jer. 14:18"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/3.43"},"Lam. 3:43"],"."]]}
